* 1939 [[James Tait Black Memorial Prize]] for ''After Many a Summer Dies the Swan''.
* 1959 Aldous Huxley [[American Academy of Arts and Letters]] Award of Merit for ''Brave New World''.
* 1962 the Companion of Literature by the [[Royal Society of Literature]].&lt;ref&gt;{{Cite book|last=Chevalier|first=Tracy|year=1997|title=Encyclopedia of the Essay|page=416|publisher=Routldge|isbn=1-57958-342-3}}&lt;/ref&gt;

