'''[[Aberdeen]]''' is a city in Scotland, United Kingdom.

'''Aberdeen''' may also refer to:
{{TOCright}}

== Aberdeen, Scotland ==
Aberdeen, Scotland, is home of:
* [[Aberdeen (HM Prison)]]
* [[Aberdeen F.C.]]
* [[Aberdeen railway station]]
* [[University of Aberdeen]]

==Africa==
;Sierra Leone
* [[Aberdeen, Sierra Leone]]
;South Africa
* [[Aberdeen, Eastern Cape]]

