* [[Aberdeen, Hong Kong]]
;Sri Lanka
* [[Aberdeen, Sri Lanka]]

==Australia==
* [[Aberdeen, New South Wales]]
** [[Aberdeen railway station, New South Wales]]
* [[Aberdeen, Tasmania]], place with a [[Scottish place names in Australia#Tasmania|Scottish placename in Tasmania, Australia]]

